data.description: Beautiful, like-new home in a newer Dinuba neighborhood is ready for its new owner! The large, open-concept layout is perfect for the whole family.. Boasting granite countertops and upgraded flooring in all living and high-traffic areas, this home will have you feeling like you bought a new house without the pain of the new construction costs and nuisances. Don't miss out on a great opportunity to get your family planted early for an awesome 2024!
